24:14.960 --> 24:15.800
SILLY DOG

24:22.320 --> 24:23.680
-Hello?
<i>-Hello.</i>

24:24.280 --> 24:26.240
<i>Have you received
your pocket money and allowance?</i>

24:29.360 --> 24:30.360
What time is your flight?

24:30.440 --> 24:31.280
I'll see you off.

24:32.760 --> 24:34.120
<i>Don't act like you care about me.</i>

24:34.200 --> 24:35.120
<i>Accept the money.</i>

24:35.200 --> 24:36.200
<i>You're scaring me.</i>

24:37.480 --> 24:38.560
Well,

24:38.640 --> 24:40.400
