24:41.520 --> 24:42.520
<i>When I have spare time.</i>

24:43.520 --> 24:44.520
<i>Don't skip meals</i>

24:44.600 --> 24:45.920
<i>and rest if you feel tired.</i>

24:47.800 --> 24:49.520
<i>Also, don't throw tantrums at Duan Jiaxu</i>

24:49.600 --> 24:50.680
<i>all the time.</i>

24:51.280 --> 24:53.480
-I never do that.
<i>-Fine.</i>

24:53.560 --> 24:56.080
-I--
<i>-Okay. I'm hanging up. Bye.</i>

25:07.800 --> 25:09.000
<i>I want</i>

25:09.080 --> 25:10.560
<i>to be more than just your boyfriend.</i>

25:12.560 --> 25:14.720
I also want to be someone you can rely on.

25:16.440 --> 25:18.480
I didn't tell you about Jiang Ying

25:19.680 --> 25:21.040
because I've grown up

25:21.120 --> 25:22.280
and I can handle it.

25:23.120 --> 25:24.680
You don't have to worry about me.

25:25.640 --> 25:28.080
I won't let her pick on me
without doing anything.

25:28.880 --> 25:30.720
I can protect myself.

25:32.440 --> 25:34.120
I can protect you too.

25:35.520 --> 25:36.680
I feel

25:38.440 --> 25:40.440
that my Zhizhi really has grown up.

25:52.840 --> 25:54.560
That concludes the product budget summary.

25:54.640 --> 25:56.160
Next, let's have our team member

25:56.240 --> 25:57.840
propose the idea for the ad.

26:00.640 --> 26:02.720
The idea for this ad

26:02.800 --> 26:05.720
uses a little girl's perspective.

26:06.280 --> 26:08.040
This little girl has suffered

26:08.120 --> 26:09.880
from allergies since childhood,

26:09.960 --> 26:12.040
so she can't eat or drink

26:12.120 --> 26:13.280
what she wants.

26:13.360 --> 26:15.720
She starts using our skincare product

26:15.800 --> 26:18.600
and is protected by a little spirit.

26:18.680 --> 26:20.040
This little spirit

26:20.120 --> 26:21.880
is a symbol of the Dongjie lotion.

26:21.960 --> 26:25.000
This ad will be about 30 seconds long.

26:25.080 --> 26:26.880
The plot revolves

26:26.960 --> 26:29.640
around the little girl and Dongjie lotion.

26:29.720 --> 26:33.000
We'll build a character image
for the users,

26:33.080 --> 26:34.680
so that the image of a little girl

26:34.760 --> 26:36.240
can always remind them of Dongjie.

26:36.320 --> 26:38.240
Aside from that,

26:38.320 --> 26:40.000
we can build a brand image

26:40.080 --> 26:41.760
to portray the traits of the brand,

26:41.840 --> 26:44.360
which are pure, gorgeous, and reassuring.

26:44.880 --> 26:46.120
Lastly, we can highlight

26:46.200 --> 26:48.600
that Dongjie is a natural product.

26:48.680 --> 26:49.560
That's the gist of it.

26:49.640 --> 26:52.440
We'll proceed with the details afterward.

26:54.680 --> 26:57.560
I like the story of the allergic girl.

27:00.320 --> 27:03.000
But I think the production fee

27:03.080 --> 27:04.760
might exceed our budget.

27:06.680 --> 27:07.840
We offer you a fair price.

27:07.920 --> 27:10.240
The difficulty comes
with the character design

27:10.320 --> 27:12.080
and the shooting.

27:12.160 --> 27:14.160
Anyway, I believe
that the more challenging it is,

27:14.240 --> 27:16.160
the more we must try it.

27:16.240 --> 27:17.360
Also, I'm confident

27:17.440 --> 27:18.960
that we can provide you

27:19.040 --> 27:21.480
with a perfect outcome.

27:22.480 --> 27:23.400
All right.

27:24.280 --> 27:25.560
We've decided

27:25.640 --> 27:27.200
to use the story of the little girl.

27:27.760 --> 27:29.120
Sir, what about the contract?

27:29.880 --> 27:31.760
Make amendments to the contract.

27:31.840 --> 27:32.880
Sign it quickly.

27:33.720 --> 27:35.280
This will be

27:35.360 --> 27:37.120
a perfect collaboration.

27:37.200 --> 27:38.520
Thank you.

27:38.600 --> 27:39.440
Let's go.

27:39.520 --> 27:41.520
-Xiaoyu, see them off.
-See them off.

27:41.600 --> 27:43.080
-This way, please.
-Okay. Be careful.

27:52.080 --> 27:52.960
Sang Zhi.

27:56.000 --> 27:57.480
You're so smart.

27:57.560 --> 27:58.920
You have an amazing brain.

27:59.000 --> 28:01.240
You're sharp as a blade,
coming up with this brilliant idea

28:01.320 --> 28:02.880
and securing this project.

28:03.360 --> 28:04.320
Do you know what this is?

28:05.080 --> 28:08.040
You've done an excellent job, rookie.

28:09.280 --> 28:10.240
If you pull your weight

28:10.320 --> 28:12.320
and do well on this proposal,

28:12.960 --> 28:15.240
I'll give the entire team a bonus!

28:16.160 --> 28:17.680
Thank you, Mr. Zhang!

28:17.760 --> 28:18.800
Brilliant, Mr. Zhang!

28:18.880 --> 28:20.200
I've never seen you all

28:20.280 --> 28:21.720
with such happy faces.

28:21.800 --> 28:22.840
You're so money-obsessed.

28:22.920 --> 28:23.760
Do your work well!

28:23.840 --> 28:24.840
-Okay!
-You've got this!

28:24.920 --> 28:26.480
-Thank you, Mr. Zhang!
-Thank you, Mr. Zhang!

28:27.720 --> 28:29.200
Sang Zhi, this is thanks to you.

28:29.280 --> 28:30.240
No problem.

28:30.840 --> 28:31.880
Xiaowan,

28:31.960 --> 28:33.840
your internship is about to be over.

28:33.920 --> 28:35.840
I'll treat you two to a meal this weekend.

28:35.920 --> 28:38.360
-Sure!
-I can't make it this weekend.

28:38.440 --> 28:39.760
I have plans.

28:39.840 --> 28:40.680
Do you?

28:41.200 --> 28:42.080
Is it a date?

28:42.720 --> 28:44.120
Why are you so nosy?

28:49.800 --> 28:51.400
I'm inside now.

28:51.480 --> 28:52.400
Where are you?

29:01.840 --> 29:02.840
I'm going to…

29:09.520 --> 29:10.440
Have you arrived?

29:15.360 --> 29:16.400
What are you doing there?

29:25.440 --> 29:27.040
Wait for me there. I'll come to get you.

29:29.200 --> 29:31.120
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

29:31.200 --> 29:32.120
Will it be…

29:39.600 --> 29:42.120
Change into slippers first.

29:55.480 --> 29:56.560
Take a look around first.

29:59.000 --> 30:00.280
There's a kitchen over here.

30:03.120 --> 30:04.920
There are two bedrooms.

30:08.840 --> 30:10.680
This room has a bigger balcony.

30:11.240 --> 30:12.200
It's your room.

30:15.240 --> 30:16.280
Does this mean

30:17.480 --> 30:19.160
that we are living together?

30:20.600 --> 30:21.680
No.

30:21.760 --> 30:24.080
I thought of giving you a place to rest

30:24.640 --> 30:26.920
when you get tired from studying.

30:31.800 --> 30:33.320
Let's go eat.

30:36.080 --> 30:36.920
By the way,

30:38.440 --> 30:40.200
you haven't told me

30:40.960 --> 30:43.120
how much the monthly rent is.

30:43.200 --> 30:44.360
Is it expensive?

30:44.960 --> 30:46.720
If it's expensive,

30:46.800 --> 30:48.360
you don't have to rent this place.

30:49.440 --> 30:50.920
Are you afraid that I can't afford it?

30:53.080 --> 30:54.000
No.

30:55.000 --> 30:56.400
I'm afraid

30:56.480 --> 30:57.520
that you are wasting money.

30:58.960 --> 31:00.480
I can afford this.

31:01.320 --> 31:03.240
I'm renting this place

31:03.320 --> 31:04.480
because it's near your campus.

31:04.560 --> 31:06.640
You can have more time to rest.

31:11.600 --> 31:12.800
Give me your hand.

31:15.640 --> 31:16.800
Why?

31:22.960 --> 31:24.160
From now on,

31:24.240 --> 31:25.640
this is our home.

32:26.160 --> 32:27.480
Hello, ma'am.

32:27.560 --> 32:29.600
This is room 202.

32:29.680 --> 32:31.840
I think something is wrong
with the air conditioner.

32:31.920 --> 32:32.840
What can I do?

32:32.920 --> 32:34.200
<i>It's summer break</i>

32:34.280 --> 32:35.640
<i>and the technician isn't on duty.</i>

32:35.720 --> 32:36.720
<i>No one can fix it.</i>

32:36.800 --> 32:38.560
<i>You'll have to wait until next semester.</i>

32:39.640 --> 32:42.240
Can I hire a technician myself?

32:42.800 --> 32:43.880
<i>I don't recommend that.</i>

32:43.960 --> 32:46.560
<i>If the fix makes it worse,
you'll have to pay for it.</i>

32:46.640 --> 32:48.080
But the room is really hot.

32:48.960 --> 32:51.360
<i>You'll have to find another solution.</i>

32:54.000 --> 32:55.520
All right. Bye.

33:13.000 --> 33:14.440
Hello, Jiaxu.

33:15.080 --> 33:16.520
What are you doing, kiddo?

33:16.600 --> 33:17.480
Have you had dinner?

33:17.560 --> 33:18.720
<i>I've eaten.</i>

33:18.800 --> 33:20.440
<i>But the air conditioner
in my dorm isn't working.</i>

33:20.520 --> 33:21.640
<i>The room is stifling.</i>

33:27.120 --> 33:28.040
I see.

33:30.560 --> 33:31.640
I'll go and fetch you now.

33:33.600 --> 33:35.200
Fetch me to go where?

33:36.200 --> 33:37.360
My place.

33:42.320 --> 33:43.560
Wait for me on campus.

33:43.640 --> 33:44.880
I'll be on my way now.

33:47.280 --> 33:48.160
All right.

34:02.400 --> 34:03.640
It's so refreshing.

34:03.720 --> 34:04.680
Here.

34:04.760 --> 34:05.880
It must be hot in your room.

34:07.840 --> 34:08.760
Change your shoes.

34:15.679 --> 34:16.560
Take a look.

34:17.040 --> 34:18.360
See what you want to eat.

34:19.840 --> 34:22.960
I bought all your favorite snacks for you.

34:27.159 --> 34:31.040
Today, I'll have this

34:31.880 --> 34:33.000
and…

34:35.960 --> 34:36.840
This.

34:36.920 --> 34:38.040
Do you want to try this?

34:43.600 --> 34:45.239
I'm all good with these.

34:46.080 --> 34:47.239
I'll eat the rest tomorrow.

34:47.760 --> 34:48.679
Okay.

34:51.400 --> 34:52.280
Have a taste.

34:56.760 --> 34:57.640
You go first.

34:57.720 --> 34:58.600
Don't you want it?

34:58.680 --> 34:59.960
You take the first bite.

35:04.160 --> 35:05.080
Is it good?

35:08.680 --> 35:10.760
You can have these every day

35:10.840 --> 35:12.120
if you move in.

35:15.320 --> 35:16.680
I'll go and tidy up the place.

35:28.400 --> 35:30.320
Do you want to take a shower?

35:30.400 --> 35:32.880
I've prepared the toiletries for you
in the bathroom.

35:38.840 --> 35:40.800
Weren't you sweating in your dorm?

35:45.440 --> 35:46.800
Go ahead and wash up.

35:47.680 --> 35:49.680
All right. I'll go now.

36:11.720 --> 36:12.800
Are you done?

36:13.360 --> 36:15.760
<i>Why did he change into pajamas?</i>

36:16.760 --> 36:17.960
Why are you standing there?

36:21.400 --> 36:23.440
I'm working.

36:27.640 --> 36:28.920
I'm playing a game.

36:31.280 --> 36:33.240
Is it the same game as before?

36:34.680 --> 36:35.800
Come and play with me.

36:43.680 --> 36:45.040
Have you tried this before?

36:49.440 --> 36:50.600
Let me show you.

36:56.680 --> 36:57.760
The first skill.

36:59.880 --> 37:01.440
Shoot. Shoot outward.

37:01.520 --> 37:02.800
The second skill is range.

37:08.320 --> 37:09.560
I'm teaching you how to play.

37:13.120 --> 37:14.200
Give it a try.

37:15.400 --> 37:16.360
Here.

37:22.120 --> 37:23.120
Buy the equipment.

37:25.560 --> 37:26.800
Attack them with the skills.

37:37.840 --> 37:39.520
Focus on the game.

37:51.480 --> 37:52.480
What should I do now?

37:54.120 --> 37:55.760
Run.

37:56.520 --> 37:57.400
Run.

37:59.320 --> 38:01.280
It's fine. You did very well.

38:01.360 --> 38:02.800
I'll go get some snacks.

38:07.080 --> 38:08.040
You…

38:08.640 --> 38:09.560
Let me see.

38:13.680 --> 38:14.640
Take your time.

38:14.720 --> 38:15.560
I…

38:17.240 --> 38:19.360
Can I unbutton it?

39:10.480 --> 39:11.680
It's done.

40:11.440 --> 40:12.560
You have

40:13.200 --> 40:14.960
to work tomorrow, right?

40:17.440 --> 40:19.200
Maybe you should go to bed now.

40:23.320 --> 40:24.200
Yes.

40:25.960 --> 40:27.760
I am a bit sleepy.

40:27.840 --> 40:30.040
I think I had better rest now.

40:30.800 --> 40:32.560
I need to go to work early.

40:36.400 --> 40:37.680
I still have some work to do.

40:44.640 --> 40:45.920
Remember to lock your door.

42:13.120 --> 42:14.240
Good morning.

42:14.320 --> 42:15.360
Good morning.

42:21.440 --> 42:23.040
I'll make breakfast for you.

42:24.400 --> 42:26.480
I'll help you.

42:47.280 --> 42:48.440
Try it.

42:51.240 --> 42:52.520
By the way,

42:52.600 --> 42:54.640
are you getting off work late today?

42:54.720 --> 42:56.480
Tell me before you leave.

42:56.560 --> 42:57.680
I'll pick you up.

42:58.240 --> 42:59.400
There's no need.

43:00.080 --> 43:01.760
I can come back myself.

43:02.840 --> 43:05.600
Also, isn't your game
going into the testing phase soon?

43:05.680 --> 43:07.800
My internship is ending soon.

43:07.880 --> 43:09.000
After that,

43:09.080 --> 43:11.920
we can have more free time to hang out.

43:12.880 --> 43:13.840
All right.

43:13.920 --> 43:16.760
When the testing phase is over,

43:16.840 --> 43:18.720
we can go anywhere you want.
